com.linecorp.armeria.server

Interface ServiceRequestContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AttributeMap, RequestContext
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultServiceRequestContext, ServiceRequestContextWrapper

    public interface ServiceRequestContext
extends RequestContext
    Provides information about an invocation and related utilities. Every request being handled has its own ServiceRequestContext instance.

      • mappedPath

        String mappedPath()
        Returns the path with its context path removed. This method can be useful for a reusable service bound at various path prefixes. For client side invocations, this method always returns the same value as RequestContext.path().

      • logger
